### 11. Inscription membre
POST {{base_url}}/members/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+22212345678",
  "full_name": "Ahmed Ould Mohamed",
  "situation": "student",
  "specialty": "Informatique",
  "study_level": "Licence 3",
  "neighborhood": "Tevragh Zeina"
}

###

### 12. Liste membres en attente (admin requis)
GET {{base_url}}/members/pending/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 13. Approuver un membre (remplace 1 par l'id réel)
PATCH {{base_url}}/members/1/validate/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"action": "approve"}

###

### 14. Rejeter un membre
PATCH {{base_url}}/members/2/validate/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"action": "reject", "rejection_reason": "Informations incomplètes."}

###

### 15. Mon profil
GET {{base_url}}/members/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 16. Modifier mon profil (PATCH partiel)
PATCH {{base_url}}/members/me/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"neighborhood": "Ksar", "job_title": "Développeur"}

###

### 17. Annuaire membres actifs
GET {{base_url}}/members/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
